caption:
@ForeverFamilyuk delivered a direct outreach service from January to March 2021 to people sleeping rough on the streets of London and Scotland. 

Delivering this service helped people in need during a once-in-a-lifetime, world changing experience of living in a National lockdown. 

@ForeverFamilyuk worked with UK charities, and international charities serving communities in Grenada, donating four barrels of clothing, sorted, sterilised, washed, dried, filled and shipped to new owners in need. 

This service met the direct needs of the public and could only have happened through the collective efforts of our communities.

We are here to serve, build and repair ✨ 

